{"tid":2155857,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官：警證供不可依賴  射水男脫襲警罪","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T10:21:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4547875d1ef9a1ec7c9baa1e82f2f7840d516c","tid":2155857,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/HP6WQ3YDENHFXFWEP326QZ6JJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FHP6WQ3YDENHFXFWEP326QZ6JJU%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR3B8Xc4SSRTU1%2BC3UxNwN9M%3D&h=390a5943\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FHP6WQ3YDENHFXFWEP326QZ6JJU%2F&h=4c0cecdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/HP6WQ3YDENHFXFWEP326QZ6JJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官：警證供不可依賴 <br />\n射水男脫襲警罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】科大生周梓樂去年11月4日在將軍澳衝突期間離奇墮樓身亡，同日凌晨亦有一名男文員被指拾起水喉向警方防線射水，其間射濕一名警長，因而被控襲警。案件昨裁決，裁判官指現場片段顯示被告不但沒有故意向警長射水，反而為免射濕警長而一度提起水喉，裁定警長的證供不可依賴，被告襲警罪不成立。被告樂見終可取回公道，稱：「法律只係將街外人帶上法庭審，但冇制度可以制裁到警隊當權」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。旁聽席上約20名聲援者聞被告獲判無罪後拍掌，被告在庭外坦言心情愉快。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3IHHitHyULsdc002O_mvCTbu7ig=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TTIIFSYW4ZFHTK7EYQZZDKUN2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3IHHitHyULsdc002O_mvCTbu7ig%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTTIIFSYW4ZFHTK7EYQZZDKUN2I.jpg&h=2b6f378b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告吳日勤由大批聲援者撐傘掩護下離開法庭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場片段顯示被告動作不明顯<br />\n<br />\n裁判官屈麗雯指，警長A是本案唯一證人，故須特別小心考慮他的供詞。A供稱。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n屈官續指，現場片段顯示被告曾提起水喉，反映他是想避免水柱射濕警長A，故不能接納控方指稱其行為罔顧後果。屈官認為，事件在短短幾秒間發生，可以理解A在電光火石之間或看不到被告曾提起水柱，惟這正正反映A的證供不可信。由於控方不能在毫無合理疑點下證明被告當時罔顧後果犯案，最終裁定被告無罪。<br />\n<br />\n控方案情指，事發時被告在警方防線前拾起水喉向警方射水，。。。。。。。。。。。為。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC1944/20"},{"pid":"52c113afcda77a7cf0a23fe6c8c30b8573131d29","tid":2155857,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95372fc66daf58466e3f13be3911410bded02337","tid":2155857,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63f0512ca9893f9a508de9b4d499c7e7a394d472","tid":2155857,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"366afd81ac23c59cd45e7757c829b1fd3f9ba13b","tid":2155857,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:21:02.000Z","msg":"大家要定時定候捐款去 612基金，長期作戰嚟。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142357</a>"},{"pid":"c871a111a75ed83d50ab4019482de455414356be","tid":2155857,"uid":43428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"做乜呢排d官正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c196a9c3d13d2598d5e62b7ca8fd86ac6c60bdba","tid":2155857,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"鍾成湧危，亂鳩咁黎"},{"pid":"b465e6586c4c1920e24e48bddc7a15cb2ec09f0f","tid":2155857,"uid":272652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"電光火石之間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3e8714df987a15bc5ea5d41a9779fbcabe5294","tid":2155857,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p